Name: Phobos
Name meaning: Greek god of fear and panic

Name: Deimos
Name meaning: Greek god of dread and terror.

Name: Europa
Name meaning: Mother of king Minos of Crete.

Name: Himalia
Name meaning: Nymph of the island of Rhodes.

Name: Elara
Name meaning: Daughter of king Orchomenus and mother of the giant Tytios.

Name: Sinope
Name meaning: Daughter of Ares and one of the Amazons.

Name: Leda
Name meaning: Aetolian princess and later Spartan queen.

Name: Thebe
Name meaning: Name used by a few of Zeus’ daughters.

Name: Metis
Name meaning: First wife of Zeus and mother of Athena.
